        <p>2. I will continue my role as an undergraduate researcher under Dr. Xiuwen Liu in conjunction with the FSU college of medicine, where we are developing an 
            interactive patient using Python (Flask) and some large language models, which medical students can use for practicing their patient assessments.
        </p>
        <p>3. I'm signed up to be a TA for an introductory programming class (COP3014).</p>
        <p>4. Aside from the 4 courses I need in order to complete my CS degree (COP4521, COP4710, CEN4090L, CIS3250L), I am also taking 2 
            advanced machine learning related courses (CIS4940 Data Mining, STA4634) in hopes of expanding my scope of knowledge in ML.
        </p>

    </div>

